<div style="margin-left:80px; margin-bottom:4em">
<div style="font-size:1.4em; font-weight:bold">[[fr/Manual/Main Page|Manuel d'utilisateur]]</div>
Le manuel fournit des informations détaillées sur la façon de jouer. Si vous découvrez le jeu, l'article [[en/Manual/Tutorial/Main Page]] vous montrera comment mettre en place votre premier service de transport, découvrez aussi le [[fr/Manual/Tutorial/Tutoriel|tutoriel]]. 

Si vous avez déjà joué à Transport Tycoon, vous aimerez alors lire la [[en/Archive/OpenTTD/Changes from TTD|comparaison entre OpenTTD et Transport Tycoon Deluxe]] pour voir les changements. Si vous connaissez le [[en/Archive/OpenTTD/TTDPatch]] qui contient quelques améliorations comme OpenTTD, regardez plutôt la [[en/Comparaison entre OpenTTD et TTDPatch]].

Enfin, pour toute question, consultez la [[fr/Archive/Community/FAQ|Foire aux Questions]].
</div>

<div style="float:left">[[File:en/Development/Code.png|64px]]</div>
<div style="margin-left:80px; margin-bottom:4em">
<div style="font-size:1.4em; font-weight:bold">[[en/Développement]]</div>
This section covers all aspects of non-graphics OpenTTD development. For those new to development, the [[en/Development/FAQ development|FAQ]] should answer any questions you have.  You can then move on to current [[en/Development/Main Page]] or helping out with [[en/Archive/Community/Internationalization|translation]] if you wish. 

You can see the [[en/Recent and Current Developments|latest developments]], [[en/Archive/Lists/Roadmap|expected features for the upcoming releases]] and the [[en/Archive/Community/Requested features]] list if you're interested in the current state of the project. If you're already a developer, the [[en/Development/Main Page]] is useful.

We also have a development community on our [[en/Development/IRC channel]] and in the [http://www.tt-forums.net/viewforum.php?f=33 development forum].
</div>

<div style="float:left">[[File:en/Community/Graphics.png|64px]]</div>
<div style="margin-left:80px; margin-bottom:1em; min-height:64px">
<div style="font-size:1.4em; font-weight:bold">[[en/Développement Graphique]]</div>
The graphics section is where artists, NewGFX engine coders, and other graphics related developers collaborate on graphics development. Find out about the latest developments in [[en/Archive/Old 32bpp/32bit Graphics Development|32bpp graphics]] (including the [[en/Community/NewGRF/Playing with 32 bpp graphics|extra zoom levels]]), [[en/Manual/NewGRF|NewGrfs]] (8bpp) and more. Also, don't forget to check the Player Resources section below for other graphics-related resources.
</div>

